3/3 Until then, please stay safe! We will see you soon! I can’t wait to come back and play for you all once again! -Pat Metheny

2/3 The good news is that we are in the process of rescheduling our concerts in May & June 2021, far enough in advance that we can hope we will face a different and safer world at that time. We will keep you posted as we confirm dates.
